Description
===========
Rossckup (A mess of Cross Backup) is a simple Perl script for cross server file/db backup, suitable for damn shared hosting environments.

Notice
======
DO NOT USE THIS SCRIPT UNLESS YOU HAVE NO RSYNC/SSH ACCESS ON YOUR HOSTING.

Dependencies
============
 - Net::FTP
 - MIME::Lite

